{"tid":1279790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所有自稱夢遊過既人同我入黎","createTime":"2019-07-02T18:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T11:46:12.000Z","uid":61032,"like":361,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"296a96d6a74a0483620e6fc91657dde0cc183e5b","tid":1279790,"uid":61032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:16:54.000Z","msg":"我知你地好多年紀都好細，可能好驚未必識應對依家既狀況<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">總之唔理出於咩原因，搵你既全部都係鬼，你地無需現身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n假如有狗上門開facebook直播當紀錄，無搜查令無拘捕令佢地乜都唔做得，呢d片段就係為左避免佢地亂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地可以做既就係處理冇用物品，同抄低律師電話，唔知搵咩人既個人建議先搵公民黨律師，無錯就係姓楊果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n需要定驚又唔知搵咩人好，我覺得可以call鄺仔、Ms Mo，電話又係事先抄定<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n電話、電腦唔好用指紋鎖，改用一般數字/英文密碼，無論咩情況下，律師未到前你唔需要講任何野<br />\n佢問乜都答：「要等律師黎」，亦唔需要解鎖任何野比佢地睇，受驚一時間忘記密碼都係好正常既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n任何時候保持冷靜，記住無論發生咩事都有我地係背後支持你地，就算要籌旗打官司都完全係濕碎野，唔使擔心呢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外無聊無野做既話，懷舊相backup出黎啦，放手指 / google drive乜都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為保持harddisk整潔，電腦手機load得快，有助你地加速收集同處理情報<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gianthang.com/technology/ins.php?index_id=54\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gianthang.com%2Ftechnology%2Fins.php%3Findex_id%3D54&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRcyEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=d59200a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gianthang.com/technology/ins.php?index_id=54</a>"},{"pid":"1590f3f20be62933fa0990ab1905530f9090f6f5","tid":1279790,"uid":61032,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:19:59.000Z","msg":"You are not Alone<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d772e8e6ba92fd85e2b1edce5547f31028901c","tid":1279790,"uid":61032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:21:51.000Z","msg":"「長期置頂」夢遊後執手尾須知<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1276769\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1276769</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f01f89296058debdc56a1c6ad7a6c95359a5b1e","tid":1279790,"uid":61032,"like":33,"dislike":2,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:24:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">總之唔理出於咩原因，刻意搵你既全部都係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"6b9b0f35bda86a4f68c2b5f77269930e4530281a","tid":1279790,"uid":61032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:27:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"494b07fc83ef1c4e8a4c450572cead2288232343","tid":1279790,"uid":272353,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:29:33.000Z","msg":"推，睇唔出係唔係三毛五毛狗就停一停，過一陣睇下回應先再推post、spread開去 廢事炒車"},{"pid":"9338c9848f4fcc6d91c69e79015b66a2b2bfe575","tid":1279790,"uid":61032,"like":83,"dislike":0,"score":83,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:29:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">假如學校有垃圾老師問你地去左邊，一律唔使回應<br />\n佢地無權管你既行踪</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as