 />\n<br />\n有咩事記住第一時間開cam，同盡力逃離現場<br />\n呢個係唯一有辦法幫到你地既手段黎，無事發生可以事後del左d垃圾片<br />\n<br />\n但萬一不幸有人傷害你地，有相有片必定追究到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf0e6e7a162dad13e2c8065756df493aa112735","tid":1279790,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:45:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e161d8f6fb597b88747cf53219ffa7c926c689f","tid":1279790,"uid":7081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:47:18.000Z","msg":"啱！"},{"pid":"13a3676675ceed3f3e3b961bdb5ce52b5f9c96eb","tid":1279790,"uid":61032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:51:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dee7054ae619073f0cc6b8a0ec3a58f1478165a","tid":1279790,"uid":61032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c3a7307fc77d6a268ec60929c136785da526e5b","tid":1279790,"uid":61032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T18:57:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"255c9acc6c766f02d36e2bc32ea57335814cd7a7","tid":1279790,"uid":61032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T19:01:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif