 xx-large;\">總之唔理出於咩原因，搵你既全部都係鬼，你地無需現身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n假如有狗上門開facebook直播當紀錄，無搜查令無拘捕令佢地乜都唔做得，呢d片段就係為左避免佢地亂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地可以做既就係處理冇用物品，同抄低律師電話，唔知搵咩人既個人建議先搵公民黨律師，無錯就係姓楊果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n需要定驚又唔知搵咩人好，我覺得可以call鄺仔、Ms Mo，電話又係事先抄定<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n電話、電腦唔好用指紋鎖，改用一般數字/英文密碼，無論咩情況下，律師未到前你唔需要講任何野<br />\n佢問乜都答：「要等律師黎」，亦唔需要解鎖任何野比佢地睇，受驚一時間忘記密碼都係好正常既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n任何時候保持冷靜，記住無論發生咩事都有我地係背後支持你地，就算要籌旗打官司都完全係濕碎野，唔使擔心呢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外無聊無野做既話，懷舊相backup出黎啦，放手指 / google drive乜都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為保持harddisk整潔，電腦手機load得快，有助你地加速收集同處理情報<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gianthang.com/technology/ins.php?index_id=54\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gianthang.com%2Ftechnology%2Fins.php%3Findex_id%3D54&d=DMh58HXBMwQbarqDBIsRcyEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=d59200a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gianthang.com/technology/ins.php?index_id=54</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T19:26:54.000Z","msg":"屌佢老尾肥柒毒MK Po義士大頭相上fb gp<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1279787\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1279787</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"52dc7ea97ab4058b33a11496447ba8151d91129c","tid":1279790,"uid":265070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T19:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936e8214cced686cd9ef1a55541b1f2d69e8e2f2","tid":1279790,"uid":85857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T19:3